entry.title: Big 5 Personality Test
entry.content:
I’m interested in tracking my personality test scores over time.

My scores on the “Big 5 Personality Test” from Truity.com:

  1. Openness: 85%
  2. Conscientiousness: 54%
  3. Extraversion: 46%
  4. Agreeableness: 75%
  5. Neuroticisim: 2%
entry.summary: I’m interested in tracking my personality test scores over time.
